{{doc/start}}
Renders a compact inline research card showing a research entry's name (linked), description, science pack costs, time per item, prerequisites, and items it unlocks. Backed by [[Module:Infobox]]'s <code>research_card</code> function. Useful for embedding a quick research summary on item or building pages.

== Usage ==
<pre>
{{Research Card|_base_research_iron_smelting}}
{{Research Card|id=_base_research_iron_smelting}}
</pre>

== Parameters ==
{| class="wikitable"
! Parameter !! Description !! Type !! Status
|-
| <code>1</code> / <code>id</code> || Research template identifier (e.g. <code>_base_research_iron_smelting</code>). || String || Required
|}

== Notes ==
* The card is styled via <code>Template:Infobox/styles.css</code> using the <code>research-card</code> CSS class family.
* The research name links to <code>NAME (Research)</code>.
* "Unlocks" lists the output items of all crafting recipes unlocked by this research, resolved via [[Module:Data/Recipes]].
* This template is distinct from [[Template:Infobox Research]] — it produces a compact inline card rather than a full infobox.
* Data comes from [[Module:Data/Research]], which is auto-generated by <code>foundry_parser generate-lua</code>.
* Typically placed in the "Research" section of item and building pages to show which research unlocks that entity.
{{doc/end}}
